### Create a new apartment with minimal required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/apartments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Minimal apartment listing",
  "basePrice": 800.00,
  "additionalCosts": 100.00,
  "rooms": 1
}

### Invalid request - missing required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/apartments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This request will fail because it's missing required fields",
  "furnished": true
}

### Health check (if actuator is enabled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json
